I '''Abdullah Öcalan''' (mibait 4 Abril 1948) metung yang kayanib a talatátag ning [[Partidung Talapagobra ning Kurdistan]] (PKK).<ref name="DoS">{{cite web| last=Powell|first=Colin |title= 2001 Report on Foreign Terrorist Organizations |url=http://www.state.gov/s/ct/rls/rpt/fto/2001/5258.htm |work=Foreign Terrorist Organizations |publisher=Bureau of Public Affairs, U.S. State Department |author=Office of the Coordinator for Counterterrorism |coauthors=Powell, Colin |location=Washington, DC |date=2001-10-05 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20020213042110/http://www.state.gov/s/ct/rls/rpt/fto/2001/5258.htm|archivedate=2002-02-13}}</ref>

Dekap de reng pwersang pangseguridad a Turkish king Nairobi i Öcalan at dela de king Turkey, nung nu ya mesentensya king kamatayan lalam ning Artikulo 125<ref>[http://www.belgenet.com/dava/gerekce19.html Belgenet Öcalan Davası Gerekçeli Karar]</ref> ning Kodigo Penal ning Turkey, a makaparikil king pamagormang gang. Miyalis ya ing sentensya king pepabayat a pang-kabangbyeng pamanyukul (''aggravated life imprisonment'') anyang leko ne ning Turkey ing parusang kamatayan king kapagnasan nang miyanib king [[European Union]]. Manibat 1999 anggang 2009, ya kabud ing presung makasukul king [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/303045.stm] isla ning [[İmralı]], king [[Sea of Marmara]].<ref>Marlies Casier, Joost Jongerden, ''Nationalisms and Politics in Turkey: Political Islam, Kemalism and the Kurdish Issue'', Taylor & Francis, 2010, [http://books.google.com.tr/books?id=_sG-NVapmrkC&pg=PA146&dq=%C3%96calan+%C4%B0mral%C4%B1&hl=tr&ei=XF3gTLC4AYWSuwO7xsW8Dg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBjgU#v=onepage&q=%C3%96calan%20%C4%B0mral%C4%B1&f=false p. 146.]</ref> Inamin nang Öcalan ing pangabayolenti ning PKK,<ref>Council of Europe, ''Parliamentary Assembly Documents 1999 Ordinary Session (fourth part, September 1999), Volume VII'', Council of Europe, 1999, [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=EkgXi4vNFjAC&pg=PA18&dq=#v=onepage&q&f=false p. 18]</ref> oneng yari na ing panaun ning armadung pamaglaban, at kaylangan yang bilugan ing pampulitikang kalutasan king pisasabyan Kurdish.<ref name="MKK">Mag. Katharina Kirchmayer, ''The Case of the Isolation Regime of Abdullah Öcalan: A Violation of European Human Rights Law and Standards?'', GRIN Verlag, 2010, [http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=E8ACMAY1rRgC&pg=PA37&dq=#v=onepage&q&f=false p. 37]</ref> Miras 40,000 a bye deng mewala king labanan ning Turkey ampo ing PKK, kayabe la reng kayabe la reng kayanib ning PKK, ing [[militar a Turkish]], ampo reng sibilyan, [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] man o [[Turkish people|Turkish]].<ref name=hurriyet9914612>{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/9914612.asp?gid=0&srid=0&oid=0&l=1 |accessdate=2008-09-17 |title=Bir dönemin acı bilançosu |work=[[Hürriyet]] |date=2008-09-16 |language=Turkish}}</ref>

Manibat king sukulan, mekapaglimbang yang mapilang libru, at ing pekabayu linwal ya anyang 2011.

